   <h1 id="2018-alumni-homecoming">
    2018 Alumni Homecoming
   </h1>
   <p>
    Spend an evening renewing acquaintances, refreshing memories, and meeting new friends.
   </p>
   <p>
    We invite all BYU Physics and Astronomy alumni and their spouse to join us for a special Physics and Astronomy homecoming reunion on
    <strong>
     Friday October 12th, 2018
    </strong>
    . Mark your calendars now and register by Tuesday October 9th to let us know which events you will be attending.
   </p>
   <h2 id="schedule">
    Schedule
   </h2>
